{"tid":1712924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中大人今晚唔好放鬆！狗多數會突襲！起碼要頂到聽朝！","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:35:28.000Z","uid":90601,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f852853a28ff623b52efc9f3b71c881749b0d953","tid":1712924,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班狗咁小學雞，唔會肯認輸<br />\n就算明知唔成功全清，都多數會突襲，拉夠人然後收隊<br />\n<br />\n大家唔會放鬆，唔好覺得有曬校長係度，可以照拉人<br />\n依家休息既休息，補充體力既補充體力<br />\n夜晚先入既手足，就幫手放哨守住先<br />\n<br />\n今晚連登手足 tg wtsapp<br />\ncall齊人聽日百萬會師<br />\n今晚仲有體力就都想辦法入去支援<br />\n小心人身安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成日話罷工有咩用？<br />\n依家話俾你知有咩用<br />\n就係拯救我地既下一代同知識份子<br />\n所有人支援暴大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"dbcf3ac547d712d2e853d678f76ca945188508b8","tid":1712924,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787767302fcd3284c980095ae40891e9e6298cb5","tid":1712924,"uid":314682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5548af12b3ce33dfe606a8305b52caaa3508870d","tid":1712924,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a251c95d911504115e945b786005524762d638f7","tid":1712924,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20